node.text:
Would you dare to live this experience? 🤪 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on worlderlust.com (link in my bio: @worlderlust)

The Pendulum Jump in Brazil is a life-changing leap that will challenge your limits. 🤯

2.5 seconds free fall over the Avencal Waterfall, a magnificient scenery that’s 100 meters high and located 10 km away from the village of Urubici, in the State of Santa Catarina. If you’re looking for a breath taking activity that brings you closer to @nature, no doubts that’s it. 🙌🏼

📽 @fragatafpv @saltodependulo

node.text:
The wonderland of Puga Valley in Ladakh, India via @apytravelstories 🤯 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting worlderlust.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @worlderlust

If you are a @nature lover, then you should really visit this place. It's incredible landscape attracts the visitors.

The Puga valley in the Changthang valley lies at about 22 km to the east of the Salt Lake valley across the Polokonka La pass (5,350 m). It is famous for its borax and sulphur deposits and hot water springs.

📽 @apytravelstories
📍 Puga Valley, Ladakh, India
🎶 Kathleen - Pure Imagination
